Instructions

Step1 create react project in bootstrap
npm i -g create-react-app

this create a react app

step 2 --------------------------------

create-react-app react_graphql
creates the react app and a folder for graph ql

use package

step 3 launch
cd react_graphql
npm start


step 4:
install grpah and the apollo graph client related plumbing

npm i -s graphql apollo-boost react-apollo
